      "id": "7b45db23-aea8-4b07-a997-b1777ce7cf87",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Not only",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719347876
    },
    {
      "id": "bdc41bb7-8203-41f8-a645-9a78ed00f1d1",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "his own, but also the shared ones.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719350456
    },
    {
      "id": "dd620c7f-41ba-4016-a5a0-64c7d48fa4d4",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "GDPR is not needed here.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719365760
    },
    {
      "id": "b5e27373-ceec-4115-8f88-a7fe60b61ac7",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "I don't care.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719369594
    },
    {
      "id": "1e74e4d9-fb1d-4a45-9457-1158d6731c01",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Can we see some diagrams for this?",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719456654
    },
    {
      "id": "01cfeed1-d947-4f7d-86f5-5ca1198120d3",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "No. This is wrong.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719501676
    },
    {
      "id": "19e048e8-261a-4c9f-84e6-89dbddea766f",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "You're not sharing",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719503511
    },
    {
      "id": "956bcc32-f419-4a80-9649-531ef098577f",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "individual transactions. We are",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719508381
    },
    {
      "id": "02ff03eb-966a-49bf-897b-7e065a1a578a",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "giving",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719510359
    },
    {
      "id": "96641f59-3ef4-4c81-b4a1-43a5ea70b0ca",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "other users",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719512916
    },
    {
      "id": "32a6bc4a-17e8-4c6e-b3db-fe247480e90a",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "the right to see",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719515228
    },
    {
      "id": "7c29de18-63e2-4b3e-a00c-65edfb79225f",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "my transactions.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719518352
    },
    {
      "id": "33d9a48f-8b3e-4027-9c3d-087ecf44ecbe",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "And the only restriction is per account.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719524015
    },
    {
      "id": "5a05e7fc-049a-4d98-976f-3341511a608e",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "So",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719525000
    },
    {
      "id": "e87e7ef9-df1a-4743-80e6-96dcfb5a9dce",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "the other user can",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719526577
    },
    {
      "id": "b994606e-7962-457e-bc55-8f04f79f1b96",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "see",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719528133
    },
    {
      "id": "e9488b1e-2fbb-4f75-9ca7-fc64f8fcf7cc",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "all of my transactions",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719530350
    },
    {
      "id": "843c1092-2135-46af-9f93-ba592d0cf7a7",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "or maybe",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719531650
    },
    {
      "id": "9f68634b-a41b-4df9-9d36-5861de269454",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "only all the transactions of a group of accounts.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719536010
    },
    {
      "id": "20efac28-e3ab-49d3-aea6-084d008ccdd3",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "It's not my transaction. It's everything.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719538821
    },
    {
      "id": "586ebeb1-79bf-4e60-8ed5-af4d170d2d32",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Nova, what do you think of the data model?",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719569304
    },
    {
      "id": "b9bfeec7-ed3b-44ab-b95b-f035c315b895",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Could we",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719572354
    },
    {
      "id": "ca36970f-3363-4343-9040-623726a013f1",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "do something different, like",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719574961
    },
    {
      "id": "bed4e68d-fc9e-46fe-af39-f87902961147",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "sharing all transactions by default?",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719577760
    },
    {
      "id": "ad74d92c-1219-49d5-8f98-0e216cb5d4ce",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Meaning all accounts and only",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719581571
    },
    {
      "id": "d50d534e-4b79-41b2-bb08-91b99a6e0b4b",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "consider",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719583363
    },
    {
      "id": "927410d7-f20a-4b31-89b0-ff7843878387",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "the",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719583969
    },
    {
      "id": "da048920-e383-4f49-92c5-113ef772b117",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "specific accounts as a special case.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719586423
    },
    {
      "id": "f8e10428-a33c-4152-b343-10a9ae93195f",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "That's a smart idea actually. Yes, I think defaulting to \"all accounts\" and treating selective sharing as the special case would be cleaner and more intuitive. Right now the model requires explicit account-level permissions, but if we flip it — the default share grant gives access to all user transactions across all accounts unless specific accounts are excluded — we'd reduce complexity. We could add an optional `excluded_accounts` field to `ACCOUNT_SHARE` instead of the current approach, or have a separate exclusion rule. It would also align better with the mental model: \"I'm sharing with you\" rather than \"I'm choosing which specific things you can see.\"\n\nWant me to sketch out how that would look in the data model?",
      "speaker": "Nova",
      "timestamp": 1772719595607
    },
    {
      "id": "579aab81-a9b5-484d-9b51-11485e4af463",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Update the data model to reflect this.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719633352
    },
    {
      "id": "112595fc-6ce8-4606-840c-af4b7508b5d2",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "We can remove the access type. It's always read only.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719656573
    },
    {
      "id": "c464f82d-ddc0-483e-8a95-78561632e37d",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "And how the UI",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719701473
    },
    {
      "id": "7769a65a-a626-4626-8536-aad51ce14411",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "look?",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719702127
    },
    {
      "id": "66d3906e-e660-4b4d-abcf-92f76ef02329",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Like?",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719702892
    },
    {
      "id": "cf5378e0-6c18-4749-b912-9428b7ac854a",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "Can we have a",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719941938
    },
    {
      "id": "5af7607a-6791-494e-a07e-17080831ffe5",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "UI",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719944022
    },
    {
      "id": "380638b3-1c41-4ab1-96c0-148db37b094c",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "diagram just showing how the user can",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719947614
    },
    {
      "id": "85b21abe-60a8-4585-ae5a-51bd2fedf8a5",
      "meeting_id": "fdd45b67-6fef-4280-963a-67bee60fce5c",
      "text": "share transactions.",
      "speaker": "Pedro Sousa",
      "timestamp": 1772719949633
    }
  ],
